Question: There is more than one animal species in the image.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://store.artwolfe.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2014/11/ZBOOAF1_00042-1024x675.jpg

Right image URL: https://images.fineartamerica.com/images-medium-large-5/grants-zebra-equus-burchelli-boehmi-art-wolfe.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many animal species are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many animal species are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} > 1 or {ANSWER1} > 1')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
